quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,"yaa-siin."
  36,2,"Mi woo…óndirii Al*ur'aana √Īe√Īaande nde."
  36,3,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), ko a jiyaa…óo e nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  36,4,"E dow laawol pocciingol."
  36,5,"Jippinannde On pool…óo, jurmotoo…óo o."
  36,6,"Fii yo a jeertinirde nde yim…ďe, …ďe baabiraa…ďe mum jerrtinanooka: …ďeen ko welsindii…ďe."
  36,7,"GooŇč…óii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe; …ďen …óoon gooŇč…óintaa."
  36,8,"Minen Min mba…óii ka daa…óe ma…ď…ďe kolommbooje, …óen ko jottii…óe ka bokku…óe; hara ko …ďe Ňčallinii…ďe."
  36,9,"Min mba…ói ye'eso ma…ď…ďe heedo, …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe kadi heedo, Min kippi …ďe (gite …óen); mba…óti …ďe nj'ataa [goonga]."
  36,10,"Hino fota e ma…ď…ďe, foti a jeertini …ďe, maa a jeertinaali …ďe; …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa."
  36,11,"Anndu ko njeertintaa (ja…ďa), ko on jokku…óo JaŇčtoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o kuli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo kaforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi."
  36,12,"Ko Minen ngoni wuurnitoo…ďe maay…ďe …ďen, Min mbinnda ko …ďe ngardini e batteeji ma…ď…ďe. Kala hu'unde, Mi…óen mofti nde e deftere …ďanngunde."
  36,13,"Piyan-…ďe yeru, fii yim…ďe saare, tuma nde Nulaa…ďe ngarunoo …ďe,"
  36,14,"Nde Min nulunoo e ma…ď…ďe, [Nulaa…ďe] …ói…óo, …ďe njeddii i …ďen, Min cammbiniri …ďen, tata…ďo, …ďe mbi'i: ""Minen, ko men Nulaa…ďe e mo'on""."
  36,15,"[Yim…ďe saare nden] wi'i: ""On ngonaani, si wanaa ko on …ďanndiŇčke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaani hay hu'unde, on wonaani, si wanaa ko on fenoo…ďe""."
  36,16,"[Nulaa…ďe …ďen] mbi'i: ""Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko min Nulaa…ďe e mo'on."
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wonaa jottingol …ďanngina""."
  36,18,"[Yim…ďe saare nden] mbi'iti: ""Min kiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on ka…óitaaki, ma min pi…óu on, lepte mu'usuu…óe kadi memira on immorde e amen""."
  36,19,"[Nulaa…ďe …ďen kadi] mb'iti: ""Kiite mon …óin, hi…óon ngon'di e mum. Ko si on mbaajaama (kiitino…óon)? Tigi on, ko on yim…ďe fantinoo…ďe!""."
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ďuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, o ari homo yaccoo, o wi'i: ""eey mon yo yim…ďe am, kori njokkee Nulaa…ďe …ďen,"
  36,21,"Njokkee …ďen …ďe la…ďndotaako on njo…ďdi, …ďen ko feewnaa…ďe."
  36,22,"E ko ha…óata kam rewugol On tak…óo Kam? Ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto dewetee…ói ga makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii kam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali kam hay hu'unde, …ói nda…óandataa kam kadi."
  36,24,"Haray miin on tuma, mi wonii e majjere …ďanngunde."
  36,25,"Min on, mi gooŇč…óinii Joomi mon, nananee kam""."
  36,26,"[O] wi'anaa: ""Naatu Aljanna"". O wi'i: ""Haaniino yim…ďe am …ďen ngannda,"
  36,27,"ko Joomi am haforani kam, O wa…ói kam e teddinaa…ďe …ďeen""."
  36,28,"Min njippiniraano koneeli ka kammu, e yim…ďe makko …ďen, …ďaawo maako. Min ngonaanii jippinoo…ďe […óin koneeli]."
  36,29,"(Halkeede ma…ď…ďe) wonaani, si wonaa haacaango wooto, tawi …ďe laatii maay…ďe-…ďutti."
  36,30,"Ee hayreede jiyaa…ďe [fenunoo…ďe]! Nulaa…óo araali e …ď…ďe, si wonaa …ďe wa…ótayno mo jalnori."
  36,31,"E …ďee njiaani …óuu…óii e gire …óe Min kalki ado ma…ď…ďe? Won'de …ďen ndttitotaako e ma…ď…ďe."
  36,32,"∆Āe fof wonaani, si wanaa ko moo…ďoytee…ďe ka amen."
  36,33,"Hino wonani …ďe Ma'ande: leydi yoorundi ndin, Min nuurniti ndi, Min njaltini gabbe e mayri, tawi ko e …óen …ďe √Īaamata."
  36,34,"Min mba…ói e mayri gese tamarooje e inabuuje, Min …ďulni e mayri …ďulli(ceewle)"
  36,35,"fii no …ďe √Īaamira dim…óe mun …óen e kon ko …ďe golliri juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen. E …ďe njettataa (Alla)?"
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii tak…óo nooneeji …óin On fof: gila e ko leydi ndin fu…óinta kon, haa e woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, e kon ko …ďe nganndaa!"
  36,37,"Ma'ande goo kadi wonanii …ďe: e jemma on, Mi…óen corta e makko √Īalawma on, tawa …ďe ngontii e niwre."
  36,38,"E na'ange ngen, hinge doga haa e √Īii…ďirde magge; …óum ko e…ď…ďoore poolu…óo, ganndu…óo On."
  36,39,"E lewru ndun, Min e…ď…ďani ndu jipporde, haa ndu wa…ótinira wa baaŇčal tamaro kii…óngal."
  36,40,"Wonaa na'ange ngen woni ko haanini hewtitagol lewru ndun, wonaa jemma on woni ko aditotoo √Īalaema on; kala majji non, ko e laawol mum woni dokde."
  36,41,"Ma'ande goo wonanii …ďe, won'de Min roondike geyngol ma…ď…ďe ngol, ka laana hebbinaaka;"
  36,42,"Min tagani …ďe sugu makko, ko …ďe mba…ó…óoo."
  36,43,"Si Mi…óen nji…óuno, Min njoolayno …ďe; hara faabo alanaa …ďe, wanaa kadi …ďe da…óndetee…ďe,"
  36,44,"si wonaa yurmeende immornde e amen, e dakmitagol haa e saanga."
  36,45,"Si …ďe mbi'anaama: ""ndentee e kon ko woni yeeso mon e …ďaawo mon, mbelajo'o, on njurminte""...!"
  36,46,"Aaya woo e aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen araali e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa …ďe …óuurnoo…óe."
  36,47,"Si …ďe mbianaama kadi: ""Wintee(nafqe) e kon Alla arsiki on"", yeddu…ďe …ďen mbi'ana gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen: ""E men √Īamminay on taw…óo si Alla muuyuno, O √Īamminayno mo? On ngonaani, si wanaa e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde""."
  36,48,"Hi…ďe mbi'a: ""Ko holnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooŇč…óu…ďe?"""
  36,49,"∆Āe habbaaki, si wonaa ha'acaango wooto, nanngayngo …ďe, hara hi…ďe njeddondira."
  36,50,"∆Āe mbaawoytaa wasiyagol on tuma, wonaa …ďe ruttoytoo…ďe e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen."
  36,51,"Wutte e alaandu, …ďe njaltira e genaale …óen, …ďe ke√Īora ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe,"
  36,52,"hi…ďe mbi'a: ""Ee bone amen! Ko hommbo immini men e genaale amen?"" Ko …óum woni ko Hinaranke On fodnoo; Nulaa…ďe …ďe o gooŇč…óini"
  36,53,"(Ummital) ngal wonaano, si wanaa haacaango wo'oto, tawi …ďe fof …ďe ngaaddaama ka Amen."
  36,54,"Hannde non, woŇčkii too√Īirtaake hay hu'unde. On yo…ďitirtaake, si wonaa kon ko ngollayno…óon."
  36,55,"Yim…ďe Aljanna …ďe hannde, pellet, he…ďe e ndeer soklio, hi…ďe neeminoo;"
  36,56,"kam…ďe e genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen,e ley …óow…óe, he…ďe co…ď…ďindii e hoore dan…óe."
  36,57,"Hino woodani …ďe toon, …ďi…ó…ďe le…ó…óe, hino woodani kadi, ko ko …ďe noddata."
  36,58,"""Salaamun"", konngol [kisal], immorde e Joomiraa…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  36,59,"""ceertee non hande, onon …ďee bon…ďe!"
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mon, onon …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama, won'de wota on ndewu seytaane? Tawde pellet, ko o ga√Īo mon …ďanngu…óo,"
  36,61,"[Mi yamiri on] kadi dewugol Kam. Ko ngol woni laawol pocciingol ngol."
  36,62,"GooŇč…óii o majjinii tagu …óuu…óungu e mon. E on wonaano haqqiloo…ďe?"
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge ngonno…óon fodaneede ngen."
  36,64,"Naatiree nge hannde, sabu ko njeddiratno…óon."
  36,65,"Hannde, Min notay e kunndule ma…ď…ďe …óen, juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yewta Min, koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen kadi seeditoo e kon ko …ďe ngonnoo e paggitagol""."
  36,66,"Si Min nji…óuno, Min mehayno gite ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe adondira e laawol ngol. Kono ko honno …ďe njiirata?"
  36,67,"Si Min nj…óuno kadi, Min montatno …ďe e nokku ma…ď…ďe on; hara …ďe hattantaa fe∆ī∆īugol …ďe yiltotaako."
  36,68,"Kala mo Min njuutni nguurndam mum, Men njiltitay mo e tagoore. E …ďee haqqiltaa?"
  36,69,"Min ngaanndinaali mo (kaŇčko Muhammadu) gim…ói; …óuum haananaa mo. [Deftere] nden wonaani, si wanaa jaŇčtoore e janngeteende …ďanngunde,"
  36,70,"fii yo o jeertin nde, on gon…óo guur…óo (…ďernde), Konngol lepte ngol jojja e he'efer…ďe …ďen."
  36,71,"E …ďe yiaani, won'de Min tagiranii …ďe neemoraa…ói, e ko juu…óe Amen ngolli, hara he…ďe njeyinoo…ói;"
  36,72,"Min eeltani …ďe …ói: no e majji …ói …ďe wa…ó…óotoo, no e majji …ói …ďe √Īaamata;"
  36,73,"hino woodani …ďe toon, nafooje e njaram. E …ďee kan njettataa (Mo)?"
  36,74,"∆Āe jogitorii ga Alla dewetee…ói, joortagol …ďe faabeedee."
  36,75,"∆äi kattanaa paabagol …ďe; ko …ďe konu tawneteengu e majji."
  36,76,"Wota konngol ma…ď…ďe sunine. Pellet, Mi…óen nganndi ko …ďe cuu…óata e ko …ďe pe√Ī√Īinta."
  36,77,"E ne…ó…óaŇčke on yiaani, won'de Min tagirii mo e to…ď…ďere maniiyu? Kono tawaa mo ko o wennjoowo …ďanngu…óo!"
  36,78,"O fiyani Min yeru, kono o yejjiti tageede makko; o wi'i: ""Ko hommbo wuurnitata ∆īi'e …óen, si …óe ndappii?"""
  36,79,"Maaku: ""Ko guurnitoowo …óe, ko tak…óo …óe on ka laawol aranol. Ko KaŇčko woni ganndu…óo fii kala tagoore;"
  36,80,"On mb…óan…óo on yiite, iwde e le…ó…óe kecce, tawa ko e majje ku…ď…ďirton nge."
  36,81,"Kere tak…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin wonaani ka…ótan…óo tagugol yeru ma…ď…ďe? ∆äuum ko pellet! Ko KaŇčko woni ∆äuu…óu…óo tageefo, ganndu…óo."
  36,82,"Ganndon fiyaaku makko on, si o faandanike hu'unde, ko o wi'anat nde tan: ""Laato"", nde laatoo."
  36,83,"Senaare woodanii oon mo laamateeri kala hu'unde ngoni e juu…óe Mum! Ko ka makko ruttete…óon."
